timeline.message: Don't wait for DB so early
Disable unit tests for now, re-order everything
Do all the other integration tests
Use older Python3 by using older Java image
Make profile for tests that require Docker
Use Dockerize for postgres, disable 2 tests

timeline.bodyText:
Does this always work? I guess so... I found out the hard way that I couldn't run on my Mac unless I added
   ulimits:
     memlock:
      soft: -1
      hard: -1

But maybe it's because I'm on a Mac.
